<br>
My guild was going after Gorenaire and we didn't like the idea of her CHing.  So me and a mage (can be any class really) got together and I kited her around.  She kept nuking me, which wasted her mana and Barrier of Force absorbed the damage.  When Barrier of Force wore off, the mage picked up the kite while I recast the epic.  Then I took over the kite again.  Well, Gore didn't CH and we owned her! =)<br>
<br>
